# kAIxU Super IDE — Build Phases
# Systematic plan to deliver every Core IDE Must-Have

Each phase ships independently and builds on the last.
All work targets the existing vanilla-JS + Netlify Functions + Neon stack.
No framework rewrites. No new bundlers. Ship fast, iterate.

---
## COMPLETION KEY
- ✅ = Fully implemented
- ⚠️ = Partially implemented (see notes)
- ❌ = Not yet implemented

