## ✅ PHASE 1 — Editor Foundation
### Goal: Replace the single-file editor with a real multi-tab, split-pane workspace

**1.1 Multi-tab editor** ✅
- ✅ Tab bar above editor (per pane, 2 panes)
- ✅ Each tab = { id, path, pane, dirty, scrollTop }
- ✅ Tabs persisted in IndexedDB (survive refresh)
- ✅ ✕ button to close; Ctrl+W closes active tab
- ✅ Unsaved indicator (dot on tab) + dirty state tracking
- ✅ Tab bar rendered independently per pane

**1.2 Split panes** ✅
- ✅ CSS flex splitter component (no library)
- ✅ Vertical split (side-by-side) via toggleSplit()
- ✅ Each pane has independent tab bar + textarea editor
- ✅ Keyboard: Ctrl+\ toggle split; Ctrl+1/2 focus pane 1/2

**Acceptance:** ✅ Can open files across 2 panes, edit independently.

