## ✅ PHASE 2 — File Explorer Upgrade
### Goal: Full file management inside the sidebar

**2.1 Rename / move / duplicate** ✅
- ✅ Right-click context menu: Rename, Move To…, Duplicate, Delete, Download, Open in split pane
- ✅ Rename: prompt input, updates open tabs
- ✅ Move: prompt for destination path, updates open tabs
- ✅ Duplicate: appends `-copy` suffix

**2.2 Drag-and-drop reorder** ✅
- ✅ File rows have `draggable="true"`
- ✅ dragstart tracks source path; dragend clears indicators
- ✅ dragover on file rows shows above/below drop indicator line
- ✅ dragover on folder rows highlights folder in purple
- ✅ drop on file → moves dragged file into same folder as target
- ✅ drop on folder → moves dragged file into that folder
- ✅ _moveFileTo() updates open tabs + re-renders tab bars

**2.3 Breadcrumb path bar** ✅
- ✅ Breadcrumb rendered per pane below tab bar (_renderBreadcrumb)
- ✅ Updates on tab switch and file open

**Acceptance:** ✅ Rename, drag-drop into folders, and breadcrumb all work without page reload.

