## ✅ PHASE 5 — Problems Panel
### Goal: Surface errors and warnings from the editor and AI

**5.1 Client-side linting** ✅
- ✅ JS: unbalanced brackets/braces/parens, debugger, console.error
- ✅ CSS: unbalanced braces, !important overuse
- ✅ HTML: unclosed tags, missing alt on img
- ✅ JSON: full parse error with line/col
- ✅ Problem shape: { file, line, col, severity, message, source }

**5.2 Problems panel UI** ✅
- ✅ "Problems" panel tab with badge count (errors + warnings)
- ✅ Severity icon + file + line:col + message
- ✅ Click row → opens file, scrolls to line
- ✅ Filter: Errors / Warnings / All
- ✅ Per-file problems replaced on re-lint

**5.3 AI-generated problems** ✅
- ✅ lintFile() called on every file open/tab switch
- ✅ Source label shown per linter (JS / CSS / HTML / JSON)

**Acceptance:** ✅ Syntax errors surface in Problems panel. Click navigates correctly.

